column5: I haven't been to this camp for a few years...any recent feedback from people that have been in the last 5 years would be appreciated.
Same business model since I started going there in 2006. Equipment and cabins are always in good shape. PjShorthorn

Last year I was there 3 times and have been going for 4 years now. Camp is about the same, great location, great cabins, great fishing. Nice amenities considering where it is. I already have 2 trips scheduled this year and absolutely love it there. If you are thinking about going back up I would not be concerned one bit.
First time for My Group last Sept... It was a huge HIT.. We booked it for same time this Sept... They WILL take care of You !!
Thanks for the response...very much appreciated.
